data.description: Welcome home to this charming and newly constructed residence nestled on Alsberry Street in scenic Strasburg, Virginia. This two story Colonial boasts the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.   Featuring three generously sized bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this home offers ample space for both relaxation and entertaining.  Enjoy the serene mountain vistas from your own private rear deck, providing an ideal setting for morning coffees or evening gatherings with family and friends. The expansive deck invites you to bask in the natural beauty that surrounds this property.  Additionally, this home includes a convenient storage building equipped with electricity, catering to various storage needs while offering versatility for hobbies or workspaces.  Embrace the allure of new construction and the tranquility of mountain views—make this home your sanctuary.
